        slug: "codesprint-7",
        name: "CodeSprint 7.0",
        description: "CodeSprint 7.0 was the biggest and most extensive event organized by a Sri Lankan university in the year 2023 with a record-breaking number of over 20 esteemed company partners and a remarkable participation exceeding 1500 participants.\n\nCodeSprint 7.0 emerged as the most funded event, captivating both sponsors and participants alike. It brought forth 300+ groundbreaking software ideas that will spark the future of technology. After facing intense competition with over 300 exceptional teams in 4 phases, the top 5 finalists have been chosen by multiple industry professionals after their innovative work was evaluated at each phase The event served as a platform for emerging tech talents to demonstrate their skills, collaborate with industry experts, and showcase their potential. The participants displayed remarkable problem-solving abilities, creativity, and a deep passion for technology.\n\nOne of the key highlights of CodeSprint 7.0 was the Grand Finale, where the top finalists pitched their groundbreaking solutions to a distinguished panel of judges. The atmosphere was electric, and the finalists' presentations left the audience in awe. The event was graced by renowned individuals from the tech giants, including CEOs and industry leaders, who witnessed the incredible talent and potential of the participants.\n\nWe are proud to share that CodeSprint 7.0 received overwhelming recognition and media coverage, which helped us reach a wide audience and establish ourselves as a leading platform for nurturing tech talent. The event garnered significant attention from industry professionals, investors, and tech enthusiasts alike.",
